<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raspadinha Premiada</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: sans-serif; text-align: center; background: #f0f0f0; padding: 20px; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 100px); gap: 10px; justify-content: center; margin-top: 20px; }
        .cell { 
            width: 100px; height: 100px; background: #999; color: white;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
            cursor: pointer; font-size: 24px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 10px;
            position: relative;
        }
        .revealed { background: white; border: 2px solid #ff5d00; }
        .logo { width: 70px; height: auto; display: none; }
        .revealed .logo { display: block; }
        .revealed .num { display: none; }
        #message { 
            margin-top: 30px; display: none; padding: 20px; 
            background: white; border: 3px solid #ff5d00; border-radius: 15px;
            max-width: 400px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1 style="color: #ff5d00;">Raspadinha Repsol</h1>
    <p>Escolhe 3 números e descobre o teu prémio!</p>

    <div class="grid" id="grid">
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">1</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">2</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">3</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">4</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">5</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">6</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">7</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">8</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">9</span><img src="https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/8e/Repsol_logo.svg/512px-Repsol_logo.svg.png" class="logo"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="message">
        <h2>🎉 PARABÉNS!</h2>
        <p>Acabaste de ganhar a obrigatoriedade de fazer um contrato Repsol hoje!</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.reload()" style="background:#ff5d00; color:white; border:none; padding:10px 20px; border-radius:5px; cursor:pointer;">Resgatar Prémio</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        let count = 0;
        function reveal(el) {
            if (!el.classList.contains('revealed') && count < 3) {
                el.classList.add('revealed');
                count++;
                if (count === 3) {
                    setTimeout(() => { document.getElementById('message').style.display = 'block'; }, 500);
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
